Creating a Todo List 
* Add an onChange event to the input. 
* Create  useStates to store the task to be added and the array of tasks.
* Add an onClick to the button.
*Write a function to handle the button click event.
* Add each task to the array of tasks after the button is clicked.
* Map through the tasks and display them on the browser.

API - Application programming interface => Any software intermediary that allows two applications to communicate with each other.
useEffect to get information from somewhere
useState to store information 
useMap to display information on a website 